  <entry>
    <title>Hexo</title>
    <link href="/2023/11/26/My-Blog/"/>
    <url>/2023/11/26/My-Blog/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="How-to-update-my-blog-simplified-version"><a href="#How-to-update-my-blog-simplified-version" class="headerlink" title="How to update my blog(simplified version):"></a>How to update my blog(simplified version):</h2><h4 id="1-Use-Git-Bash-here-at-My-Blog-file"><a href="#1-Use-Git-Bash-here-at-My-Blog-file" class="headerlink" title="1. Use Git Bash here at My Blog file"></a>1. Use Git Bash here at My Blog file</h4><h4 id="2-Override-the-default-port-4000-change-it-to-5000"><a href="#2-Override-the-default-port-4000-change-it-to-5000" class="headerlink" title="2.Override the default port (4000), change it to 5000"></a>2.Override the default port (4000), change it to 5000</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo s -p 5000<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3-enter-the-web-and-add-admin-to-revise-My-Blog"><a href="#3-enter-the-web-and-add-admin-to-revise-My-Blog" class="headerlink" title="3. enter the web and add &#x2F;admin to revise My Blog"></a>3. enter the web and add &#x2F;admin to revise My Blog</h4><h4 id="4-generate-the-up-dated-imformation-and-put-them-into-public"><a href="#4-generate-the-up-dated-imformation-and-put-them-into-public" class="headerlink" title="4. generate the up-dated imformation and put them into public"></a>4. generate the up-dated imformation and put them into public</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo g<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="5-put-publish-into-github"><a href="#5-put-publish-into-github" class="headerlink" title="5. put publish into github"></a>5. put publish into github</h4><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">$ hexo d <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Andthen your blog will be revised and you can visit it at swjtu.beauty.</p><p>You need to wait sometime to see the changes.</p>]]></content>
    
    
